# Icon Set

**Figma:** [Qure Icon Set](https://www.figma.com/design/AW4jk9SLPKlSqYt6NZ1QK5/Qure-%3C%3E-Figma-Design-system?node-id=7809-18809&p=f&m=dev)

Sizes, colors, and categories below are derived from Figma node 7809:18809.

---

